Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,310)\fsp15\an8\fad(300,0)\bord1\1c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(0,326,848,370)}斬斷絕望
